directed graph and fd is a deployment selection map such that fd : V ‚Üí D. A concrete workÔ¨Çow W is sensible for W0
if the function that maps a deployment to a service is compatible with the function that selects a service for each node.
In the absence of speciÔ¨Åc requirements or constraints, W is feasible for W0 if it is sensible for W0 , i.e. all possible
combinations are in principle acceptable.
